snippet.title: Android/iOS Strategy Idle Game "Rogue with the Dead" Promotion Video
snippet.description:
Rogue with the Dead is an original roguelike RPG where you command and power up troops on an endless, looping journey.
What kills you makes you stronger.

Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.room6.horizon

App Store
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-rogue-with-dead/id1515542137
